George Kerevan: The outbreak of Europe gives the Scottish people a choice
Another day, another disturbing story of independence.
This time, we are told that an independent Scotland would be required to join the European free movement zone in order to join the EU.
And here we hear stories of passport control in Berwick and a border of barbed wires along the Hadrian wall.
